| Category         | Tools / Libraries                                   |
|------------------|-----------------------------------------------------|
| Frontend         | Streamlit                                           |
| NLP Model        | `facebook/bart-large-cnn` via `transformers`        |
| Audio Transcribe | `whisper`                                           |
| Language         | Python 3.8+                                         |

